<STARTDOC>
macro(htmlbodyopt(option)(value))
(Adds tt(option="value") to the options of the tt(<body ...>) tag in HTML
files. Useful options are, e.g., tt(fgcolor) and tt(bgcolor), whose values
are expressed as tt(#rrggbb), where tt(rr) are two hexadecimal digits of
the red component, tt(gg) two hexadecimal digits of the green component,
and tt(bb) two hexadecimal digits of the blue component.)
<>

DEFINEMACRO(htmlbodyopt)(2)(\
<html>
    ADDTOSYMBOL(XXbodyopt)( ARG1=CHAR(")ARG2+CHAR("))\
<>
)

